Well, Doctor, it appears that the designers of this site wanted a dialog.  Admittedly, this dialog got a little personal at times.  But in a passionate debate one does not think logically.  If nothing else, before you ride off into the smoggy sunset of So. Cal.; I must say that you certainly stimulated debate.  Look at this thread.  The most responses of any.  Sometimes being a straw man generates things that would not be under normal circumstances. Then again that may have been your purpose all along. Who knows?  Not I!  You made me put thoughts down that I certainly have never written before.  For that I thank you.  All pomposity aside; remember &quot;The easy way is always mined.&quot; Stay in touch.
